     C* E17: record-identification codes select record types.
     C* Col 1 = '1' -> indicator 01; col 1 = '2' -> indicator 02.
     FRIDATA  IP  F    80              DISK
     FRIOUT   O   F    132             PRINTER
     IRIDATA      011    C1
     I            021    C2
     I                                     2   4   0VAL       02
     C  02                 ADD  VAL       RPGRET
